        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Generating Synthetic Data\n",
        "\n",
        "- A simple nonlinear function  \n",
        "- Add noise to simulate real data  \n",
        "- We’ll use kernel regression to approximate it  "
      ],
      "id": "7b3217b4"
