    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Nadaraya–Watson Attention Pooling\n",
        "\n",
        "- Each validation point is a [query]{.uured-bold}  \n",
        "- Each training point is a [key–value pair]{.uured-bold}  \n",
        "- The normalized kernel weights are [attention weights]{.uured-bold}  "
      ],
      "id": "0d9e9340"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| echo: false\n",
        "#| eval: true\n",
        "\n",
        "def nadaraya_watson(x_train, y_train, x_val, kernel):\n",
        "    dists = x_train[:, None] - x_val[None, :]\n",
        "    k = kernel(dists)\n",
        "    weights = k / k.sum(dim=0, keepdim=True)\n",
        "    y_hat = y_train @ weights\n",
        "    return y_hat, weights"
      ],
      "id": "96869b38",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
