        "\n",
        "## Kernel Width Matters\n",
        "\n",
        "- Narrow kernels → sharp, local attention  \n",
        "- Wide kernels → smooth, global attention  \n",
        "- Small $\\sigma$ → attention collapses to nearest neighbors  \n",
        "- Large $\\sigma$ → attention spreads across many points  \n"
      ],
